dataset.attr: FIO-ESM model output prepared for CMIP5 historical

variable.long_name: Water Evaporation Flux Where Ice Free Ocean over Sea
variable.attr: computed as the total mass of water vapor evaporating from the ice-free portion of the ocean divided by the area of the ocean portion of the grid cell.
time: mean area: mean where ice_free_sea over sea

variable.long_name: Water Flux into Sea Water From Rivers
variable.attr: computed as the river flux of water into the ocean divided by the area of the ocean portion of the grid cell.
time: mean area: mean where sea

variable.long_name: Water Flux into Sea Water due to Sea Ice Thermodynamics
variable.attr: computed as the sea ice thermodynamic water flux into the ocean divided by the area of the ocean portion of the grid cell.
time: mean area: mean where sea

variable.long_name: Downward Heat Flux at Sea Water Surface
variable.attr: "This is the net flux of heat entering the liquid water column through its upper surface (excluding any ""flux adjustment"") ."
time: mean area: mean where sea

variable.long_name: Rainfall Flux where Ice Free Ocean over Sea
variable.attr: computed as the total mass of liquid water falling as liquid rain into the ice-free portion of the ocean divided by the area of the ocean portion of the grid cell.
time: mean area: mean where ice_free_sea over sea

variable.long_name: Snowfall Flux where Ice Free Ocean over Sea
variable.attr: computed as the total mass of ice directly falling as snow into the ice-free portion of the ocean divided by the area of the ocean portion of the grid cell.
time: mean area: mean where ice_free_sea over sea
"This is defined as ""where ice_free_sea over sea"""
time: mean area: mean where ice_free_sea over sea

variable.long_name: Net Downward Shortwave Radiation at Sea Water Surface
variable.attr: This is the flux into the surface of liquid sea water only. This excludes shortwave flux absorbed by sea ice, but includes any light that passes through the ice and is absorbed by the ocean.
time: mean area: mean where sea
